{
  "texts": [
    "• A new fusion strategy IF-VMD-FSRA-CNN for short PV power assessment is optimized to generalize and improve predicting efficiency in a variety of meteorological conditions.",
    "• The assessment and interpretation of several decomposition methods for short-term PV-plants power fore- casting.",
    "• The fusing of multi-scale features from the employed decomposition techniques for boosting the forecasting precision of PV power output.",
    "• Using a feature selection technique allows users to choose the most meaningful intrinsic function IMFs from various multi-scale methodologies, which improves forecasting ability and minimizes the dimensionality of the data.",
    "• The deep CNN model is capable of deriving deeper characteristics from the fused multi-scale information to provide the appropriate PV output power."
  ]
}